And no its not a &#039;&#039;DC&#039;&#039; 

He said &#039;&#039;GG gl getting promoted&#039;&#039;

&#039;&#039;A summoner has been disconnected&#039;&#039;

Alright. now there is a 3-0 brand and a missing teammate.

''But my premade will abuse this''

How. Losing 40 LP instead of 20 cant be abused. You are literally losing half a division at that point.



EDIT: For the people saying ''amg this will be exploited'' Then everyone in the premade will have to lose equal LP. So if your teammate dcs you are taking a heavier responsibility for that if he was your premade.

There now you have to actually be cautious of who you play with.
